      • toScriptBindings

        Bindings toScriptBindings(ScriptEngine engine,
                        ScriptContext newContext,
                        Bindings bindings,
                        int engineScope)
        Convert a set of bindings to a more scripting-language-friendly object.

        This is called twice, once for bindings at ScriptContext.GLOBAL_SCOPE, and again for bindings at ScriptContext.ENGINE_SCOPE.
